    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚央行讨论加息，并承诺警惕持续通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/australia-holds-key-rate-at-12-year-high-on-inflation-worries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚央行周二讨论了加息的可能性，随后决定将当前利率维持在 12 年来的最高水平，因为政策制定者试图在顽固的通胀和疲软的经济之间取得平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/australia-holds-key-rate-at-12-year-high-on-inflation-worries</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 04:33:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行行长警告不要重新设定通胀目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/thai-central-bank-chief-warns-against-tweaking-inflation-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行行长进一步反对政府提高货币当局通胀目标的建议，并指出此举将给东南亚第二大经济体带来风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/thai-central-bank-chief-warns-against-tweaking-inflation-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 03:48:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非政府合作伙伴准备展开内阁之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨 (Cyril Ramaphosa) 准备宣誓就职，但由于 5 月 29 日的选举未能产生绝对胜利者，南非各政党上周同意组成执政联盟，并准备在内阁职位上展开争夺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/south-african-elections-new-government-partners-eye-cabinet-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>危机加深 他信、泰国总理陷入法律诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦因侮辱王室一案面临审判，而最高法院命令他的盟友兼总理斯雷塔·达维辛提交更多证据以要求罢免他，这一举动加剧了这个东南亚国家的政治危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-17/thaksin-set-for-indictment-as-court-weighs-thai-premier-s-future</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
